description: Embark on a fiery flavor adventure with our spicy Pani Puri! Crispy puris filled with zesty masala, tangy tamarind water, and a kick of spice that will awaken your taste buds. It's not just a snack; it's a taste explosion in every bite! ?????

Transport yourself to the streets of Kolkata with our classic old Gol Gappa. These crispy, hollow puris are filled with a delightful mixture of tangy tamarind water, spicy masala, and the authentic taste of tradition. Indulge in the timeless joy of every bite! ?????

Dive into the refreshing burst of flavors with our Jaljeera Fuchka! Crispy puris, generously filled with a tantalizing mix of cool jaljeera water, tangy spices, and a hint of mint. It's not just a snack; it's a symphony of taste that will leave you craving more. Experience the joy of every flavorful pop! ?????

Indulge in the perfect blend of textures and tastes with our Doi Fuchka! Crispy puris, delicately filled with a luscious mixture of creamy yogurt, tangy tamarind chutney, and a medley of spices. Each bite is a harmonious dance of flavors, creating a sensation that's both refreshing and satisfying. Experience the joy of this delightful treat! ?????

Elevate your taste experience with our Chana Masala Fuchka! Crispy puris filled with a delectable mix of spiced chickpeas, tangy tamarind chutney, and aromatic masalas. It's a flavor-packed journey that takes the classic fuchka to new heights, promising a burst of savory goodness in every bite. Spice up your palate with this delightful twist! ?????
